{"tid":271948,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"冇利好消息照炒！比特幣急飆近7%　再撲新高 (20:17)","createTime":"2017-06-05T13:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T13:00:57.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e233690a8ccca1789091c38c12fe0faa91328b89","tid":271948,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T13:00:57.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=sCdFQRGDBylZsrJLvB35p9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=4c1d480c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】比特幣再次撲向新高！最新報2,597美元，急升6.84%，若以此價位收市的話，將創下收市新高，而盤中新高為2,798美元。<br />\n<br />\n市場人士表示，今日並沒有明顯的催化劑令比特幣急升，估計是上周中國政府放寬了3大比特幣平台提幣後的餘波，為今年2月以來首次，意味着中國政府放鬆了資本管制。 <br />\n<br />\n事實上，隨着日本政府接受比特幣，加上俄羅斯最大網上零售商Ulmart亦宣布接受比特幣付款，均令需求急增。比特幣今年以來已累飆1.7倍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170605/20170605201718fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170605%2F20170605201718fi.html&d=sCdFQRGDBylZsrJLvB35p9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=62c144ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170605/20170605201718fi.html</a>"}]}